The '''''Redma''''' was a [[Galactic Federation of Free Alliances|Galactic Alliance]] [[Cruiser/Legends|cruiser]] assigned to the [[Fifth Fleet (Galactic Alliance)|Fifth Fleet]]. It was destroyed during the [[Battle of Kashyyyk (Second Galactic Civil War)|Battle of Kashyyyk]] following a sustained barrage from the [[Bothan/Legends|Bothan]] navy.

